      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im in dubai right now just got off a crazy long flight from nyc. my chest kinda hurts with every breath and i feel super short of breath. i think the travel stress is just giving me a massive panic attack lol. do u have any tips to calm down the anxiety so i can sleep?",
